<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Definitely. Complicated relationships between Thomas Jefferson and the secret family he had with one of his many slaves. Several of his children with <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Definitely. Complicated relationships between Thomas Jefferson and the secret family he had with one of his many slaves. Several of his children with Sally Hemmings looked just like him and later when freed, lived as free white citizens. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
