      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12196419-amanda-m-the-curly-reader?shelf=middle-grade">middle-grade</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12196419-amanda-m-the-curly-reader?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12196419-amanda-m-the-curly-reader?shelf=owned">owned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12196419-amanda-m-the-curly-reader?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>
