<div id="review_2341907516" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2341907516" />
    <a title="Amy-Jo Conant" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/60159532-amy-jo-conant"><img alt="Amy-Jo Conant" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1523114021p2/60159532.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2341907516?book_show_action=true">May 14, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amy-Jo Conant" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amy-Jo Conant" href="/user/show/60159532-amy-jo-conant">Amy-Jo Conant</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2341907516" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14146140165078700898">Teen or YA book<br/><br/>I love historical fiction but even if you don&apos;t I think many students would enjoy this book. The book requires a level of maturity to deal with issues such as slavery and mature adult relationships.<br/><br/>Your eyes will be opened to a part of history that many people are unaware of. The book invites the reader to look at a dark part of our American History and evaluate an American Hero through a new lens. <br/><br/>This book stimulates both your mind and heart. </span>
  <span id="freeText14146140165078700898" style="display:none">Teen or YA book<br /><br />I love historical fiction but even if you don't I think many students would enjoy this book. The book requires a level of maturity to deal with issues such as slavery and mature adult relationships.<br /><br />Your eyes will be opened to a part of history that many people are unaware of. The book invites the reader to look at a dark part of our American History and evaluate an American Hero through a new lens. <br /><br />This book stimulates both your mind and heart. </span>
