      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/14631537-jefferson-s-sons">Quotes from Jefferson&#39;s Sons</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;What you know in your head and what you say out loud are not always the same.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
